{"tid":1190403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十年“浮瓜”Extras","createTime":"2019-06-07T09:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T09:54:21.000Z","uid":50457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"26982e404f875c5caf2570011d1004e78636b384","tid":1190403,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:47:15.000Z","msg":"浮瓜 Extras<br />\n片段採用黑白畫面拍攝。講述2020年五一勞動節慶活動期間，一所中學的禮堂正舉行由建制派政黨舉辦的蛇齋餅糭活動。與此同時，樓上課室有多名政界高層、警隊以及黑社會，計畫射傷兩位建制派議員以製造混亂，激起港人恐懼，從而加速中央實施「國安法」。兩名黑社會「炒散」獲分配「任務」，眼見可觀酬勞，決定孤注一擲執行任務，卻沒料想到最後被警方槍殺。這一連串的計劃目的只是在於令「國安法」成功通過。[11]。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4_(%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25B9%25B4_%28%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%29&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uoeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=fef4b9e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4_(%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1)</a>"},{"pid":"1db9e0c67460bf541613caef334c40609288fe2b","tid":1190403,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:50:58.000Z","msg":"屌我都諗起呢集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff54559709d127a3437e3f2df7c091a0eca4bc5f","tid":1190403,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1db9e0c67460bf541613caef334c40609288fe2b","tid":1190403,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:50:58.000Z","msg":"屌我都諗起呢集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:54:21.000Z","msg":"十年電影好多嘢，發生緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}